token_lists.title: Magik Spheres
token_lists.description: A collection of magic orbs, painted directly on video. Each piece made individually by the artist.

token_lists.title: Sandstorm Series
token_lists.description:
Created to explore the possibilities of digital painting using video, Sandstorms are made of textures and fluid shapes to suggest an abstract universe. 
Not generative, each piece was made individually by the artist.
